      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">About Arqwell</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-3">Arqwell is a resource hub for architects who want to use artificial intelligence in real projects. We focus on training, tools, and workflows instead of hype.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-3">Our tools connect AI to Rhino, Revit, and Dynamo so you can ask questions in plain language and receive ready to test scripts and workflows. You remain the designer. AI is your technical assistant.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">We support working and emerging professionals in the AEC field who need reliable methods, documentation, and repeatable processes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-5 text-sm text-slate-800 space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">What we offer</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>AI training specific to architecture and BIM workflows</li>
          <li>Plug-ins that were designed and built with AI support</li>
          <li>Chat based assistants for Dynamo and Rhino Python</li>
          <li>Templates, prompts, and example projects you can reuse</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
