      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Arqwell Plug-in Downloads</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-3">Download and install the Arqwell Assistant plug-ins for Revit and Rhino to use the chat-based AI assistant directly inside your design software. Ask questions, generate scripts, and get Dynamo or Python code within your active model.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-800 space-y-1.5 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Revit Assistant</strong> – Use natural language to create Dynamo scripts, automate model setup, and run AI-generated routines without leaving Revit.</li>
          <li><strong>Rhino Assistant</strong> – Chat in Rhino to generate Python scripts, automate geometry, or prototype Grasshopper logic in seconds.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="#" class="px-4 py-2.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white hover:bg-slate-800">Download for Revit</a>
