        <p class="font-semibold text-slate-600 text-sm mb-1">How it works</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
          <li>1. Download and install the plug-in for your software.</li>
          <li>2. Log in with your Arqwell account.</li>
          <li>3. Open the chat sidebar and type your request in plain language.</li>
          <li>4. The Arqwell Assistant generates a Dynamo or Python script, ready to run or test in your file.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Future updates will add Grasshopper integration and shared cloud libraries for scripts generated by the community.</p>
