          <li><span class="font-semibold">Prompts:</span> Share your favorite prompt for cleaning a Revit model.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[0.7rem] text-slate-500">In a live version, this area can display recent threads from your subreddit using the Reddit API so visitors can see active conversations without leaving the site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dummy contact anchor for nav + modal trigger -->
  <section id="contact" class="h-0 w-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true"></section>

  <!-- TRAINING MODAL (Arqwell Sessions) -->
  <div id="training-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 hidden items-center justify-center bg-black/40">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 max-w-lg w-full mx-4 p-6 relative">
      <button id="training-modal-close" class="absolute top-3 right-3 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-700 text-sm">✕</button>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-slate-500 mb-2">Arqwell Sessions</p>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Upcoming live training</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-4">Live sessions that walk through how to install and use Arqwell plug-ins in Rhino, Revit, and Dynamo. Join from anywhere and follow along with sample files.</p>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-3 bg-slate-50">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Next session</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Arqwell Sessions: Dynamo + Revit Automation</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-700">Demo of the Dynamo chat workflow, renaming sheets, and creating a lighting layout script.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">Date: <span class="font-medium">TBD – add your preferred dates in the form below.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Coming soon</p>
