      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Contact Arqwell</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-4">Please fill out the short form below to connect with us. You will receive an automated confirmation letting you know that we’ve received your message and will respond soon.</p>
      <iframe src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_ID/viewform?embedded=true" title="Arqwell Contact Form" class="w-full h-96 border-0 rounded-xl"></iframe>
